descriptionNullable:
Labeled images of characters from the anime, K-On!!. Each image (.jpg, .png) matches to a label (.txt) file of the same name that designates the position of ground truth bounding boxes in that image. Currently available characters and their class label include the following:
0 - Hirasawa Yui
1 - Tainaka Ritsu
2 - Kotobuki Tsumugi
3 - Akiyama Mio
4 - Nakano Azusa
This is detailed in the classes.txt file.
